// Build configuration applied at the project level via project.yml's
// `configFiles` block. Inherited by every target (iOS app, macOS app, tests,
// frameworks) unless a target-level setting overrides a specific key.
//
// Shared settings that should apply to every checkout go directly in this
// file. Per-developer values (currently: DEVELOPMENT_TEAM) live in a
// gitignored Local.xcconfig that is conditionally included below, so each
// developer's signing team selection stays out of shared history.
//
// On a fresh checkout Local.xcconfig does not exist; the `#include?`
// (note the trailing `?`) is optional and silently skipped, leaving
// DEVELOPMENT_TEAM unset. Signing will fail until the developer copies
// Local.xcconfig.example to Local.xcconfig and fills in their team ID.

#include? "Local.xcconfig"
